{
  "id": "adv_event_2301_01_01",
  "title": "今年最後のライブバトル",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――I-UNITY後、初めての年末",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The first year-end after I-UNITY",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 2.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "おおっ！　大阪は久しぶりですね～\nくんくん……早くもお好み焼きの香りが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! It's been a while since we've been to Osaka.\nSniff… I can already smell the okonomiyaki.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9,
      "endTime": 12.238458061200001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ、本当に？　私、何も感じないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? I don't feel anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4333333333,
      "endTime": 16.7378456433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "この雑多な感じがいいよね。活気がある\nライブにはもってこいの街だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like this lively atmosphere. This is energetic and\na perfect city for a live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9333333333,
      "endTime": 23.5564655457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。今年最後のライブよ\nきっちり気合いを入れていきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it is. It's our last live performance this year.\nLet's put all our effort into it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7666666667,
      "endTime": 29.1618321737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "合同カウントダウンライブ、私達はメインを\n飾るんですもんね！　嫌でも気合いが入ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a joint countdown live‚ and we are the main act!\nWe have to be pumped up whether we like it or not!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3666666667,
      "endTime": 36.0922708466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルはないけど、他の事務所のアイドル達と\n比較されるからね。無様なステージは出来ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There may not be a live battle‚ but we'll still be compared to idols\nfrom other agencies‚ so we can't have an ordinary stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2666666667,
      "endTime": 44.4968056927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！　最高のステージにするために\nこころから素晴らしい提案がありまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright! To make it the best stage ever‚\nKokoro has a fantastic proposal!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7,
      "endTime": 52.064603042600005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "却下よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Denied.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2,
      "endTime": 53.1922902465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで、聞きもしないで却下なんですかぁ！？\nっていうか、そんないい笑顔で言わないで下さい～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why?! Why are you rejecting it without even hearing me out?!\nAnd please don't say it with such a nice smile…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5666666667,
      "endTime": 60.228184409600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "どうせ……\nこころがセンターをやりまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because…\nKokoro will be the center!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4333333333,
      "endTime": 64.5046428244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "こころのアイドルスマイルで\n大阪のファンはイチコロですよ♪",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With Kokoro's idol smile‚\nOsaka's fans will be won over!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9333333333,
      "endTime": 69.6238095749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "――とか、言うんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Is what you were going to say‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8333333333,
      "endTime": 71.0146938642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "こころがセンターをやりまーす！　……はっ！？\nこころが言おうとしたことをなぜ？　超能力！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro will be the center!… Huh?!\nWhy did you say what Kokoro was going to say?! Is it telepathy?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2,
      "endTime": 79.6332650821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "いつもこころが言ってることだからだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because Kokoro-chan always says the same thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9333333333,
      "endTime": 82.9738094647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "それにこころの物真似に悪意が感じられるんですけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ your impersonation of me feels malicious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1666666667,
      "endTime": 87.8369612376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "それはともかく、意気込みはいいんじゃない？\n僕達は仲間だけど、ライバルでもあるんだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ it's good to have enthusiasm‚ right?\nWe are friends‚ but we are also rivals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.0333333333,
      "endTime": 96.0861179723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "センターがほしいなら、先輩も後輩も関係ない\n実力で相手をねじ伏せて、奪い取ればいい。ね、莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you want to be the center‚ it doesn't matter if you're a senior or a junior.\nIf you want it‚ prove it with your skills. Right‚ Rio-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3,
      "endTime": 106.668913269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、こころも愛も\nいつでも挑戦しにきていいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right. Kokoro-chan and Ai-chan‚\nfeel free to challenge us anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8666666667,
      "endTime": 111.8958862702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえいえ！　滅相もないです！\n私は端っこで結構です！　うう、先輩方の圧が怖い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ no! No need for that!\nI'm fine on the sidelines! The pressure from you seniors is scary…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1,
      "endTime": 120.68815611549999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "こころ的には実力はあと一歩で莉央さんに届く\n感じなんですけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In Kokoro's opinion‚ I'm just one step away from reaching\nRio-san in skill‚ you know…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9,
      "endTime": 127.2038570881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、そこは愛嬌でカバーするということで\n一度くらいはセンターを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I guess I'll make up for it with my charm.\nAt least once‚ let me be the center…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4,
      "endTime": 133.3576259439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ、会場に向かいましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's head to the venue now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5333333333,
